description: Beautiful one bedroom, one full bathroom unit in Macallen Building is available June 1. This bright unit features a contemporary kitchen with island and room for four stools. A large living room can easily accommodate dining room table and full living room set. Bedroom with tons of closet space featuring custom build-outs to maximize the storage space. Bamboo hardwood flooring throughout living space. Washer/dryer in-unit. Dual zone heating and cooling, and one garage parking space included. Building offers high end amenities including: 24/7 concierge, in-ground heated lap pool, common terrace with BBQ gas grills and free WiFi on terrace, fitness center, and common bike storage.
